OL,3,CWoman says government is 'punishing
OL,4,Cpensioners' with winter fuel payment
OL,5,Ccuts
OL,7,FAn 85-year-old woman from Bristol says
OL,8,Fshe feels betrayed by government plans
OL,9,Fto cut winter fuel payments to
OL,10,Fmillions of pensioners across the
OL,11,Fcountry.
OL,13,FOn Tuesday 10 September, MPs voted to
OL,14,Fapprove government plans to cut the
OL,15,Fwinter fuel payment for most
OL,16,Fpensioners.
OL,18,FI an annual, tax-free sum of between
OL,19,F#200 and #300, intended to give older
OL,20,Fpeople reassurance that they can
OL,21,Fafford to heat their homes in winter.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
