OL,7,FA total of 348 MPs voted against the
OL,8,Fmotion and 228 MPs voted in favour of
OL,9,Fit.
OL,11,FSir Keir Starmer has justified the
OL,12,Fplans to help "secure the foundations"
OL,13,Fof the economy, but backbench MPs,
OL,14,Funion leaders, and the opposition have
OL,15,Fall called on the government to
OL,16,Freverse the decision.
OL,18,FSpeaking before the vote took place,
OL,19,FSir Keir said it was a "really tough
OL,20,Fdecision".
