OL,3,CWoman says government is 'punishing
OL,4,Cpensioners' with winter fuel payment
OL,5,Ccuts
OL,7,FLike many across the country, Judith
OL,8,FBrown from Bristol will miss out this
OL,9,Fyear. She doesn't qualify for pension
OL,10,Fcredits but says she's far from being
OL,11,Fwealthy.
OL,13,FShe said: "I feel betrayed. I never
OL,14,Fthought a Labour Government would do
OL,15,Fthis - punish the pensioners instead
OL,16,Fof people who've got lots of money. Or
OL,17,Fthe energy companies who make billions.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
