OL,5,Ccuts
OL,7,F"I turn everything off at night. I
OL,8,Funplug everything. I don't use the
OL,9,Foven very much because it takes so
OL,10,Fmuch electricity.
OL,12,F"So many of us are doing everything we
OL,13,Fcan to keep the cost down, but we do
OL,14,Frely on that money."
OL,16,FAlison Davies from Weston-super-Mare
OL,17,Fis another person affected by the
OL,18,Fpayment.
