OL,5,Ccuts
OL,7,FShe's one of many who've been
OL,8,Fsupported by the local group Burnham
OL,9,Fand Weston Energy to help keep bills
OL,10,Fdown over the winter.
OL,12,FShe said: "They've talked to me about
OL,13,Fhow I keep warm and how I stop drafts
OL,14,Fand things coming in.
OL,16,F"But this is an old house and it does
OL,17,Ftake a lot of energy to keep it
OL,18,Freasonably warm."
