OL,3,CWoman says government is 'punishing
OL,4,Cpensioners' with winter fuel payment
OL,5,Ccuts
OL,7,FPhil Dolan, CEO of Age UK Somerset,
OL,8,Fsays charities may also lose out on
OL,9,Fdonations from pensioners who don't
OL,10,Fneed the allowance.
OL,12,FMr Dolan said: "Wealthier pensioners
OL,13,Fwhen they get the #300 will happily
OL,14,Fdonate that money to charity.
OL,16,F"We can then redistribute that money
OL,17,Fto pensioners where that money doesn't
OL,18,Ftouch the sides of the bills that
OL,19,Fthey're facing."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
